# A-CMO-BrandTuner Technical Logic Specification

## 1. System Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     A-CMO-BrandTuner Core Engine                    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐              │
│  │ Brand Signal │  │  Sentiment   │  │  Competitive │              │
│  │  Ingestion   │──│   Analysis   │──│   Indexing   │              │
│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘              │
│         │                 │                 │                       │
│         ▼                 ▼                 ▼                       │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐       │
│  │              Brand Health Score Calculator               │       │
│  │         BHS = Σ(wᵢ × Sᵢ) / Σwᵢ × (1 - DegradationFactor)│       │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘       │
│         │                                                           │
│         ▼                                                           │
│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐              │
│  │   Tuning     │  │  Threshold   │  │   Alert      │              │
│  │   Engine     │──│   Evaluator  │──│   Dispatcher │              │
│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 2. Core Mathematical Models

### 2.1 Brand Health Score (BHS)

```
BHS(t) = (α × Awareness(t) + β × Sentiment(t) + γ × Engagement(t) + δ × Loyalty(t)) / (α + β + γ + δ)

Where:
  α = 0.25 (Awareness weight)
  β = 0.30 (Sentiment weight)
  γ = 0.25 (Engagement weight)
  δ = 0.20 (Loyalty weight)

Normalized Range: [0.0, 1.0]
```

### 2.2 Brand Velocity Index (BVI)

```
BVI(t) = (BHS(t) - BHS(t-Δt)) / Δt

Where:
  Δt = measurement interval (default: 24h)

Interpretation:
  BVI > 0.05  → Positive momentum
  BVI ∈ [-0.05, 0.05] → Stable
  BVI < -0.05 → Negative momentum (trigger alert)
```

### 2.3 Competitive Position Score (CPS)

```
CPS = (BHS_self - μ_competitors) / σ_competitors

Where:
  μ_competitors = mean BHS of competitor set
  σ_competitors = standard deviation of competitor BHS

Z-score interpretation:
  CPS > 2.0  → Market leader
  CPS ∈ [0, 2.0] → Above average
  CPS ∈ [-2.0, 0] → Below average
  CPS < -2.0 → Critical position
```

### 2.4 Tuning Coefficient Calculation

```
TuneCoeff(channel) = (TargetBHS - CurrentBHS) × ChannelElasticity(channel) × BudgetConstraint

ChannelElasticity:
  Social    = 0.15
  Search    = 0.12
  Display   = 0.08
  Email     = 0.10
  Content   = 0.18
  PR        = 0.22
```

