## 3. Breakdown Point Score (BPS) Matrix

### 3.1 BPS Calculation Formula

```
BPS(component) = Σ(Pᵢ × Iᵢ × Dᵢ) / 100

Where:
  Pᵢ = Probability of failure (0-100)
  Iᵢ = Impact severity (1-10)
  Dᵢ = Detection difficulty (1-10)

Risk Classification:
  BPS ∈ [0, 50)    → LOW
  BPS ∈ [50, 150)  → MEDIUM
  BPS ∈ [150, 300) → HIGH
  BPS ≥ 300        → CRITICAL
```

### 3.2 Component BPS Matrix

| Component | Failure Mode | P (0-100) | I (1-10) | D (1-10) | BPS | Risk Level |
|-----------|--------------|-----------|----------|----------|-----|------------|
| Data Ingestion Pipeline | Source API timeout | 35 | 8 | 3 | 84 | MEDIUM |
| Data Ingestion Pipeline | Schema drift | 25 | 9 | 7 | 157.5 | HIGH |
| Data Ingestion Pipeline | Rate limit exceeded | 45 | 6 | 2 | 54 | MEDIUM |
| Sentiment Analyzer | Model degradation | 20 | 8 | 8 | 128 | MEDIUM |
| Sentiment Analyzer | Language detection failure | 15 | 5 | 4 | 30 | LOW |
| Sentiment Analyzer | Context misclassification | 40 | 7 | 9 | 252 | HIGH |
| BHS Calculator | Weight misconfiguration | 10 | 10 | 6 | 60 | MEDIUM |
| BHS Calculator | Null signal propagation | 25 | 9 | 5 | 112.5 | MEDIUM |
| BHS Calculator | Temporal alignment drift | 30 | 7 | 8 | 168 | HIGH |
| Tuning Engine | Recommendation oscillation | 35 | 8 | 7 | 196 | HIGH |
| Tuning Engine | Budget constraint violation | 20 | 9 | 4 | 72 | MEDIUM |
| Tuning Engine | Channel elasticity stale | 45 | 6 | 6 | 162 | HIGH |
| Alert Dispatcher | Notification queue overflow | 25 | 7 | 3 | 52.5 | MEDIUM |
| Alert Dispatcher | Threshold false positive | 50 | 4 | 5 | 100 | MEDIUM |
| Alert Dispatcher | Escalation path failure | 15 | 10 | 4 | 60 | MEDIUM |
| Database Layer | Connection pool exhaustion | 20 | 9 | 3 | 54 | MEDIUM |
| Database Layer | Replication lag > 30s | 30 | 8 | 4 | 96 | MEDIUM |
| Database Layer | Index corruption | 5 | 10 | 8 | 40 | LOW |
| Cache Layer | Cache stampede | 25 | 7 | 5 | 87.5 | MEDIUM |
| Cache Layer | Stale data serving | 40 | 6 | 7 | 168 | HIGH |
| External Dependencies | Social API deprecation | 10 | 10 | 2 | 20 | LOW |
| External Dependencies | Third-party rate limiting | 55 | 5 | 2 | 55 | MEDIUM |

### 3.3 Aggregate System BPS

```
System_BPS = Σ(Component_BPS × CriticalityWeight) / Σ(CriticalityWeight)

Component Criticality Weights:
  Data Ingestion Pipeline  = 1.5
  Sentiment Analyzer       = 1.3
  BHS Calculator           = 1.8
  Tuning Engine            = 1.6
  Alert Dispatcher         = 1.0
  Database Layer           = 1.4
  Cache Layer              = 0.9
  External Dependencies    = 1.2

Current System_BPS = 127.4 (MEDIUM)
```

